OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,FJoshua had climbed onto the tracks
OL,7,Fafter shouting that he wanted to kill
OL,8,Fhimself.
OL,10,FSenior Coroner Jacqueline Devonish
OL,11,Fconcluded Joshua's death was by
OL,12,Fmisadventure, while Jordan's death was
OL,13,Fan accident.
OL,15,FDuring the inquest, she told Jordan's
OL,16,Ffamily: "I know that you wanted him to
OL,17,Fbe hailed as a hero for what he did.
OL,18,FWell he was a hero.
OL,20,F"His act of selflessness in trying to
OL,21,Fsave his friend is to be commended."
OL,26,@|D@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
