OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,FMs Devonish said Joshua lost his life
OL,7,Fwhen he climbed down onto the railway
OL,8,Fline at Poynton into the path of an
OL,9,Foncoming train.
OL,11,FShe said: "Joshua was shouting that he
OL,12,Fwanted to kill himself and he climbed
OL,13,Fdown from the platform, but there was
OL,14,Fno evidence that he intended to take
OL,15,Fhis own life. But rather was under the
OL,16,Finfluence of alcohol that caused him
OL,17,Fto be impulsive."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,FOn Jordan, the coroner recorded a
OL,7,Fverdict of accidental death, adding:
OL,8,F"He was actively trying to stop
OL,9,FJoshua. Jordan was shouting at Joshua,
OL,10,Ftelling him to get off the track.
OL,11,FJordan wanted to save his friend. He
OL,12,Fjumped back down on the track and
OL,13,Ftried to push his friend to safety.
OL,15,F"He was acting solely about saving his
OL,16,Ffriend, but they could not move fast
OL,17,Fenough with the train moving at speed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,FThe court heard that Joshua was drunk
OL,7,Fand shouting he wanted to kill himself
OL,8,Fwhen he climbed down from a platform
OL,9,Fand onto the live rail tracks.
OL,11,FA friend who was with them both, who
OL,12,Fcan't be named for legal reasons, told
OL,13,Fpolice that Jordan "tried to rugby
OL,14,Ftackle" Joshua "onto the other side of
OL,15,Fthe tracks".
OL,17,FHe said in the statement: "Jordan was
OL,18,Ftrying to save him. I know he was.
OL,19,FJordan was shouting at him. If Jordan
OL,20,Fdid not care he would not have got
OL,21,Fonto the tracks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,F"Them two did everything together.
OL,7,FThey died together as well."
OL,9,FHe said Joshua jumped onto the tracks
OL,10,Fand told how he dragged him back onto
OL,11,Fthe platform, before he jumped down
OL,12,Fagain as the train approached.
OL,14,FHe said: "It comes around the corner,
OL,15,Fthe train. I have seen it hit them
OL,16,Fboth. I thought Jordan might have been
OL,17,Fclipped. I have waited. I could not
OL,18,Fsee Josh."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,FThe friend, who was also 16 at the
OL,7,Ftime, said Joshua was "bladdered" and
OL,8,Fdid not really want to take his own
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FHe said: "It was an accident because
OL,12,Fhe did not know that the train was
OL,13,Fcoming. Jordan was screaming at him to
OL,14,Fget off, but he just wouldn't."
OL,16,FThe inquest heard they were hit by an
OL,17,FAvanti train heading to Manchester
OL,18,FPiccadilly from London Euston. Both
OL,19,Fteenagers were said to have suffered
OL,20,Fmultiple traumatic injuries
OL,21,F"incompatible with life".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,FIn a statement, Jordan's mum, Nicola
OL,7,FEverett, said her son was trying to
OL,8,Fsave Joshua.
OL,10,F"Jordan lost his life in doing so,"
OL,11,Fshe said. "The least that can be done
OL,12,Ffor Jordan now is to give him the
OL,13,Frecognition for what he was trying to
OL,14,Fdo.
OL,16,F"Jordan lost his life trying to save
OL,17,FJoshua. His bravery should be known.
OL,18,FWe are proud of our son, but
OL,19,Fdevastated beyond belief.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,F"Our lives are devastated. Jordan's
OL,7,Fact of selflessness and his bravery
OL,8,Fshould be known and commended."
OL,10,FJordan's father said the 16-year-old
OL,11,Fwas about to start a course in
OL,12,Fengineering at Manchester College and
OL,13,Fwanted to be a pilot.
OL,15,FThe court heard he volunteered with a
OL,16,Frescue dog charity in Bulgaria and was
OL,17,Fan RAF cadet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771963514
OL,3,C'Hero' teen died trying to save friend
OL,4,Cfrom train
OL,6,FHis father Paul Everett said: "He grew
OL,7,Finto a caring, sociable young man with
OL,8,Fa wide circle of friends. He always
OL,9,Fput others before himself."
OL,11,FIn a statement, Joshua's mum, Jenny
OL,12,FMyers, said: "Joshua did not want to
OL,13,Fdie. I know he would have been
OL,14,Fterrified. His death was not something
OL,15,Fthat he wanted or planned.
OL,17,F"I believe he was failed by every
OL,18,Fservice he came into contact with. He
OL,19,Fwas a vulnerable child who needed help
OL,20,Fand we sought to get him that help."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
